  <div class="box en">🎯 <strong>What to watch:</strong> ① Whether the new agreement's common share price and PIPE size shrink materially from the original terms ② Whether a concrete new deadline is set, or the deal drifts again with no timetable ③ Whether other bitcoin-treasury SPAC deals begin renegotiating on the same grounds ④ How Strategy's and Metaplanet's mNAV levels feed into the deal's eventual pricing</div>
